quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  24,54,"Maaku: "∆äoftee Alla …óofto…óon Nulaa…óo on". Si …ďe nduŇčtiima anndu ko fawii mo ko, ko o roondaa kon, no fawii on ko ndoonda …óo kon, si on …óoftike mo on peewat, fawaaki Nulaa…óo on si wonaa jottinngol …ďanngungol."
  24,55,"Alla Fodii …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe e moo…óon …ďe ngolli mo∆ī∆īi …óin o lomtinat …ďe ka leydi wano O lomtinirnoo non …ďen adii…ďe …ďe, ma O wee…ďinan …ďe diina ma…ď…ďe ka O welanaa …ďe, ma O wattitan …ďe …ďaawo kulol ma…ď…ďe ngol hoolaare, Yo …ďe ndewam wota …ďe cirkanam hay e hu'unde. Kala jeddu…óo …ďaawo …óum haray …ďen …óon ko kam…ďe woni faasiqii…ďe …ďen."
  24,56,"√Ďii…ďee e Juulde totton askal on …óofto…óon kadi nulaa…óo on, mbela jo'o on njurmete."
  24,57,"Wota a sikku …ďeen yeddu…ďe …ďe laawoto ka leydi, jaa∆īorde ma…ď…ďe nden ko ka Yiite, pellet, bonii wattnde."
  24,58,"Eey mon yo gooŇč…óin…ďe, yo sakkintino e moo…óon …ďen …ďe √Īaame moo…óon jeyi, e …ďen …ďe njottaaki koy…óol immorde e moo…óon, laabi tati ko adii Juulde Peeral nden, e tuma mballinton conci moo…óon ka njollooro e ka …ďaawo Juulde gee∆īe ko awraaji moo…óon tati non. Bakkaatu fawaaki on fawaaki …ďe …ďaawo majji, jinndoo…ďe hakkunde moo…óon, yoga e moo…óon e dow yoga. Ko wano nii Alla …ďanngini- rani on aayeeje …óen Alla ko O ganndu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo."